[size=6][center][color=#f39c12][b]!!! This is only the Base Framework !!![/b][/color]

[color=#e74c3c][b]You will need to download [color=#f39c12][i]Weapon Add-On Packs[/i][/color] in addition to this mod.[/b][/color][/center][/size][b][color=#f4f4f4][size=6]
[center]About this Framework[/center][/size][/color][/b]This is an all-in-one Gun Framework for [i]Blade & Sorcery[/i] which supports manual reloading for pistols, shotguns, SMGs and Rifles. 

With on-going development for secondary fire attachments, explosives, and NPC waves, this framework is constantly under development and will evolve as [i]Blade & Sorcery[/i] receives updates.


[center][b][color=#2ed573][size=6][u]Install Instructions[/u]
[/size][/color][/b]
[size=5][i][color=#ffe599]Extract the downloaded zip file and copy this folder:[/color][/i]

[color=#2ed573][code]ModularFirearmsFramework
[/code][/color]
[i][color=#ffe599]into this directory (your BAS Mods folder):[/color][/i]

[color=#2ed573][code] \Blade & Sorcery\BladeAndSorcery_Data\StreamingAssets\Mods\ 
[/code][/color][/size][/center]

[size=5][b]To Download Weapons[/b], you can either check the "Requirements" section of this mod to find other mods requiring this framework, or you can choose from this list:
[/size]

[size=6][color=#f39c12][b][center]Modular Addon Packs Available ($GLOB_GAME_VERSION)[/center][/b][/color][/size][quote]
